  <title translate="true">Classes</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Classes</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Header 2" style="text-align:right;"><link displaytype="image" src="New_Back_Arrow_icon.gif" type="topiclink" href="Support"></link><text styleclass="Header 2" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true"> </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Support" styleclass="Answer" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true">Return to Support Menu</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I add a new class to the system?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to add a new class to the system please follow the directions below.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Support</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Add</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter the information on the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">profile</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> screen</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Save</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Once you have saved the profile information for the class you have added a &quot;shell&quot; for the class.  The next step is to add teachers and students.  Adding teachers and students to a class are both covered in the next two FAQ, please follow from step 6 to the end for both &quot;How do I add teachers to a class&quot; and &quot;How do I add students to a class&quot;.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I add teachers to a class?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to add teachers to a class please follow the steps below.  If you are adding teachers to an already created class please start at step 1.  If you have just added the class and are on the profile screen please start at step 6.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Support</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Class</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Use the criteria to search for the desired class.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Edit</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Icon</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> for the desired class</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Add</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teacher</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Name</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">school</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> etc. to narrow the search results</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Check the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">box</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> next to the desired teacher(s)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">When the teacher has been chosen Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Select</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Return to Class</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">Multiple teachers can be added to a class.  The first teacher added to a class will be marked as the primary teacher, any additional teacher will be treated as a secondary.  The Reset Primary option on the Teachers tab of the class will allow you to change the primary teacher if desired.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I add students to a class?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to add students to class please follow the steps below.  If you are adding students to an already created class please start at step 1.  If you have just added the class and are on the profile screen please start at step 6.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Support</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Class</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Use the criteria to search for the desired class</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Edit</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon for the class the student(s) will be added to</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Add</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter criteria to find the  desired student(s)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Check the box next to the desired student(s) </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">Multiple students can be selected</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Select</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Return to Class</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I delete a class?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to delete a class please follow the directions listed below:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="8" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Support</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Use the Criteria to find the class to be deleted</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Edit</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Icon</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> next to the class to be deleted</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to completely delete a class the Students and Teachers must be removed first.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="8" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> in the left nav</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Hover over </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Actions</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> and select </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Check</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">All</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Remove</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Teachers</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> in the left nav</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Hover over </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Actions</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> and select </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Check</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">All</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Remove</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Students</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Profile</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> in the left nav</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Delete</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Class</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[What does "Retain on Resync" mean?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">If a class is marked as &quot;Retain on Resync&quot; it means that the next roster load will not delete the class.  If this option is not checked for a class, the class will be removed when the next roster file is imported.  We strongly recommend making sure this box is checked if you do not want the class to be deleted during the next import.  If the class is deleted it will need to be manually added back after the import.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I find the assessments available to a class?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Test events for a particular class can be viewed from within the class &quot;edit&quot; screen.  In order to locate and view these test events please follow the directions below:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="20" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Support</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> Icon</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Use the criteria to search for the desired class</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Classes</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Choose the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Edit</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Icon</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> next to the desired class</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Test</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Events</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> from the Class Profile Screen</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">The Test Events tab will display all assessments available to the class.  If you wish to administer one of these assessments click the dashboard for the desired event.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
